\": 2305}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2325}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2339}, {\"ngram\": \"young kids\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2355}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the first ever Olympic facility of its kind.\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2407, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first ever Olympic facility\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2394}, {\"ngram\": \"its kind\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why create this space?\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2431, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this space\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2430}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why is it needed?\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2450, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ALLYSON FELIX: Yes, when I came back from competition after having my daughter, it was really challenging.\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2558, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ALLYSON FELIX\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2465}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2505}, {\"ngram\": \"my daughter\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I had a hard time traveling around with her and competing.\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2622, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hard time\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And so when I was appointed on the Athletes Commission of the IOC, it was really top of mind to figure out, how can we better support mothers?\", \"from\": 2624, \"to\": 2766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Athletes Commission\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2678}, {\"ngram\": \"the IOC\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2689}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2716}, {\"ngram\": \"mothers\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And when we thought about the Olympic Games, it felt like this is something that should have been done a long time ago.\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2887, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2811}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And we are just so proud that now there is a space in the athlete village to be able to bring your babies, your young children, to spend time with them, bond with them and also just get away from the pressures of the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 2889, \"to\": 3120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a space\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 2939}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete village\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 2962}, {\"ngram\": \"your babies\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 2994}, {\"ngram\": \"your young children\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3015}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3026, \"to\": 3030}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressures\", \"from\": 3085, \"to\": 3098}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3102, \"to\": 3119}]}, {\"sentence\": \"AMNA NAWAZ: Tell me about that time when you came back after you had your first daughter in 2018.\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3219, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3122, \"end\": 3132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amna_Nawaz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AMNA NAWAZ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amna_Nawaz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amna_Nawaz\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that time\", \"from\": 3148, \"to\": 3157}, {\"ngram\": \"your first daughter\", \"from\": 3191, \"to\": 3210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You competed in Tokyo in 2021 after that.\", \"from\": 3221, \"to\": 3262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3237, \"end\": 3242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999985866926164, \"rank\": 1.4123701931080155e-06, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With a young child, what was hard about that?\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3309, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a young child\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What were the challenges?\", \"from\": 3311, \"to\": 3336, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the challenges\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ALLYSON FELIX: Yes, when I went back to competition, it was flying with an infant.\", \"from\": 3338, \"to\": 3420, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ALLYSON FELIX\", \"from\": 3338, \"to\": 3351}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 3378, \"to\": 3389}, {\"ngram\": \"an infant\", \"from\": 3410, \"to\": 3419}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was going to competitions, sometimes being assigned a roommate or having to wash bottles in hotel rooms.\", \"from\": 3422, \"to\": 3529, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 3438, \"to\": 3450}, {\"ngram\": \"a roommate\", \"from\": 3477, \"to\": 3487}, {\"ngram\": \"bottles\", \"from\": 3506, \"to\": 3513}, {\"ngram\": \"hotel rooms\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, just some of the smaller practical things that were challenging.\", \"from\": 3531, \"to\": 3599, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the smaller practical things\", \"from\": 3548, \"to\": 3576}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And so we just want to figure out a way, how can we show up and how can we support mothers to make it easier so that they can know they are just as capable to have these big-time performances after childbirth.\", \"from\": 3601, \"to\": 3810, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 3635, \"to\": 3640}, {\"ngram\": \"mothers\", \"from\": 3684, \"to\": 3691}, {\"ngram\": \"these big-time performances\", \"from\": 3765, \"to\": 3792}, {\"ngram\": \"childbirth\", \"from\": 3799, \"to\": 3809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"AMNA NAWAZ: We mentioned this is the first-ever facility of its kind.\", \"from\": 3812, \"to\": 3881, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3812, \"end\": 3822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amna_Nawaz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AMNA NAWAZ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amna_Nawaz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amna_Nawaz\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first-ever facility\", \"from\": 3845, \"to\": 3868}, {\"ngram\": \"its kind\", \"from\": 3872, \"to\": 3880}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why did it take so long?\", \"from\": 3883, \"to\": 3907, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ALLYSON FELIX: I really think maybe a lack of having mothers at the table.\", \"from\": 3909, \"to\": 3983, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lack\", \"from\": 3945, \"to\": 3951}, {\"ngram\": \"mothers\", \"from\": 3962, \"to\": 3969}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 3973, \"to\": 3982}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think there is a lot of people who have paved the way for something like this to happen, pieces in place.\", \"from\": 3985, \"to\": 4096, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 4006, \"to\": 4011}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4015, \"to\": 4021}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 4037, \"to\": 4044}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 4049, \"to\": 4058}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 4090, \"to\": 4095}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And, finally, it came around.\", \"from\": 4098, \"to\": 4127, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was shocked that when I brought it up before the commission, it was so well-received.\", \"from\": 4129, \"to\": 4216, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the commission\", \"from\": 4176, \"to\": 4190}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And we moved really quickly on it.\", \"from\": 4218, \"to\": 4252, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I think sometimes we just need more voices, more stories amplified.\", \"from\": 4254, \"to\": 4325, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more voices\", \"from\": 4289, \"to\": 4300}, {\"ngram\": \"more stories\", \"from\": 4302, \"to\": 4314}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think now, more than ever, we are seeing so many athlete mothers competing and doing so well that we are really trying to shift the culture.\", \"from\": 4327, \"to\": 4473, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many athlete mothers\", \"from\": 4374, \"to\": 4397}, {\"ngram\": \"the culture\", \"from\": 4461, \"to\": 4472}]}, {\"sentence\": \"AMNA NAWAZ: And you have been one of those leading voices when it comes to calling for that support that you know mothers need.\", \"from\": 4475, \"to\": 4602, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4475, \"end\": 4485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amna_Nawaz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AMNA NAWAZ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amna_Nawaz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amna_Nawaz\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those leading voices\", \"from\": 4512, \"to\": 4532}, {\"ngram\": \"that support\", \"from\": 4562, \"to\": 4574}, {\"ngram\": \"mothers\", \"from\": 4589, \"to\": 4596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And you quoted someone else saying that basically having a baby in track and field was once called the kiss of death, meaning that your competing career was over.\", \"from\": 4604, \"to\": 4766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 4619, \"to\": 4626}, {\"ngram\": \"a baby\", \"from\": 4661, \"to\": 4667}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 4671, \"to\": 4676}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 4681, \"to\": 4686}, {\"ngram\": \"the kiss\", \"from\": 4703, \"to\": 4711}, {\"ngram\": \"death\", \"from\": 4715, \"to\": 4720}, {\"ngram\": \"your competing career\", \"from\": 4735, \"to\": 4756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have two children of your own now, but you very bravely called out your then-sponsor of Nike back in 2019 for their maternity policy.\", \"from\": 4768, \"to\": 4905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4860, \"end\": 4864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9278157456761007, \"rank\": 0.07780010535002702, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two children\", \"from\": 4777, \"to\": 4789}, {\"ngram\": \"your then-sponsor\", \"from\": 4839, \"to\": 4856}, {\"ngram\": \"their maternity policy\", \"from\": 4882, \"to\": 4904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You wrote an op-ed at the time -- quote -- \\\"If we have children, we risk pay cuts from our sponsors during pregnancy and afterward.\", \"from\": 4907, \"to\": 5038, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an op-ed\", \"from\": 4917, \"to\": 4925}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 4929, \"to\": 4937}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 4962, \"to\": 4970}, {\"ngram\": \"pay cuts\", \"from\": 4980, \"to\": 4988}, {\"ngram\": \"our sponsors\", \"from\": 4994, \"to\": 5006}, {\"ngram\": \"pregnancy\", \"from\": 5014, \"to\": 5023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's one example of a sports industry where the rules are still mostly made for and by men.\\\"\", \"from\": 5040, \"to\": 5132, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one example\", \"from\": 5045, \"to\": 5056}, {\"ngram\": \"a sports industry\", \"from\": 5060, \"to\": 5077}, {\"ngram\": \"the rules\", \"from\": 5084, \"to\": 5093}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 5127, \"to\": 5130}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Allyson, you basically forced Nike to rewrite their maternity policy.\", \"from\": 5134, \"to\": 5203, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5164, \"end\": 5168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9278157456761007, \"rank\": 0.07780010535002702, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their maternity policy\", \"from\": 5180, \"to\": 5202}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But at the time, how hard was it to come out and say what you did?\", \"from\": 5205, \"to\": 5271, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 5212, \"to\": 5220}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ALLYSON FELIX: Yes, it was terrifying.\", \"from\": 5273, \"to\": 5311, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ALLYSON FELIX\", \"from\": 5273, \"to\": 5286}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I mean, for me, I am a person who I do not really like to rock the boat.\", \"from\": 5313, \"to\": 5385, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a person\", \"from\": 5334, \"to\": 5342}, {\"ngram\": \"the boat\", \"from\": 5376, \"to\": 5384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have not been in the past very outspoken.\", \"from\": 5387, \"to\": 5430, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And it was just going through this very real-life situation that I realized I have to say something.\", \"from\": 5432, \"to\": 5532, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this very real-life situation\", \"from\": 5462, \"to\": 5491}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 5522, \"to\": 5531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had a traumatic birth experience with my daughter and it happened over the same course of this time.\", \"from\": 5534, \"to\": 5636, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a traumatic birth experience\", \"from\": 5540, \"to\": 5568}, {\"ngram\": \"my daughter\", \"from\": 5574, \"to\": 5585}, {\"ngram\": \"the same course\", \"from\": 5607, \"to\": 5622}, {\"ngram\": \"this time\", \"from\": 5626, \"to\": 5635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I felt like that gave me that last bit of courage and that last push that I needed to say there is no way I am going to allow my daughter and her generation to take on this same fight.\", \"from\": 5638, \"to\": 5826, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that last bit\", \"from\": 5667, \"to\": 5680}, {\"ngram\": \"courage\", \"from\": 5684, \"to\": 5691}, {\"ngram\": \"that last push\", \"from\": 5696, \"to\": 5710}, {\"ngram\": \"no way\", \"from\": 5741, \"to\": 5747}, {\"ngram\": \"my daughter\", \"from\": 5768, \"to\": 5779}, {\"ngram\": \"her generation\", \"from\": 5784, \"to\": 5798}, {\"ngram\": \"this same fight\", \"from\": 5810, \"to\": 5825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I really wanted to stand up for myself and other female athletes.\", \"from\": 5828, \"to\": 5893, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other female athletes\", \"from\": 5871, \"to\": 5892}]}, {\"sentence\": \"AMNA NAWAZ: And that traumatic birth experience with your daughter, you have also talked about.\", \"from\": 5895, \"to\": 5990, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5895, \"end\": 5905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amna_Nawaz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AMNA NAWAZ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amna_Nawaz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amna_Nawaz\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that traumatic birth experience\", \"from\": 5911, \"to\": 5942}, {\"ngram\": \"your daughter\", \"from\": 5948, \"to\": 5961}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You had severe preeclampsia, which we know is a condition that puts Black women in particular at five times a higher risk of death than white women in America.\", \"from\": 5992, \"to\": 6151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6007, \"end\": 6019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pre-eclampsia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"preeclampsia\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pre-eclampsia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pre-eclampsia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a condition\", \"from\": 6038, \"to\": 6049}, {\"ngram\": \"Black women\", \"from\": 6060, \"to\": 6071}, {\"ngram\": \"five times a higher risk\", \"from\": 6089, \"to\": 6113}, {\"ngram\": \"death\", \"from\": 6117, \"to\": 6122}, {\"ngram\": \"white women\", \"from\": 6128, \"to\": 6139}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 6143, \"to\": 6150}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I also want to note you were just awarded some $20 million by Melinda French Gates, a philanthropist, in a maternal health grant.\", \"from\": 6153, \"to\": 6282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6215, \"end\": 6235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melinda_French_Gates\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Melinda French Gates\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melinda_French_Gates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melinda_French_Gates\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a philanthropist\", \"from\": 6237, \"to\": 6253}, {\"ngram\": \"a maternal health grant\", \"from\": 6258, \"to\": 6281}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What do you want to do with that?\", \"from\": 6284, \"to\": 6317, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What are your plans for those funds?\", \"from\": 6319, \"to\": 6355, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your plans\", \"from\": 6328, \"to\": 6338}, {\"ngram\": \"those funds\", \"from\": 6343, \"to\": 6354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ALLYSON FELIX: Yes, I was so humbled to be selected as a leader to be able to deploy these funds.\", \"from\": 6357, \"to\": 6454, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ALLYSON FELIX\", \"from\": 6357, \"to\": 6370}, {\"ngram\": \"a leader\", \"from\": 6412, \"to\": 6420}, {\"ngram\": \"these funds\", \"from\": 6442, \"to\": 6453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I really want to focus on Black maternal health.\", \"from\": 6456, \"to\": 6508, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Black maternal health\", \"from\": 6486, \"to\": 6507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, we are under the umbrella of women's health.\", \"from\": 6510, \"to\": 6565, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the umbrella\", \"from\": 6534, \"to\": 6546}, {\"ngram\": \"women's health\", \"from\": 6550, \"to\": 6564}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I really want to find organizations that are doing important and urgent work and have an impact really on the communities and the people who are most at risk.\", \"from\": 6567, \"to\": 6729, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"organizations\", \"from\": 6593, \"to\": 6606}, {\"ngram\": \"important and urgent work\", \"from\": 6622, \"to\": 6647}, {\"ngram\": \"an impact\", \"from\": 6657, \"to\": 6666}, {\"ngram\": \"the communities\", \"from\": 6677, \"to\": 6692}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 6697, \"to\": 6707}, {\"ngram\": \"risk\", \"from\": 6724, \"to\": 6728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I am so excited to put these funds to use and to identify these organizations who will really be game changers.\", \"from\": 6731, \"to\": 6845, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these funds\", \"from\": 6757, \"to\": 6768}, {\"ngram\": \"these organizations\", \"from\": 6792, \"to\": 6811}, {\"ngram\": \"game changers\", \"from\": 6831, \"to\": 6844}]}, {\"sentence\": \"AMNA NAWAZ: So you are at these Games as a spectator.\", \"from\": 6847, \"to\": 6900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6847, \"end\": 6857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amna_Nawaz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AMNA NAWAZ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amna_Nawaz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amna_Nawaz\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 6873, \"to\": 6884}, {\"ngram\": \"a spectator\", \"from\": 6888, \"to\": 6899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We all just saw Noah Lyles win gold in the 100 meters, Sha'Carri Richardson take silver.\", \"from\": 6902, \"to\": 6990, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6918, \"end\": 6928, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 6957, \"end\": 6977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sha'Carri Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 6933, \"to\": 6937}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100 meters\", \"from\": 6941, \"to\": 6955}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 6983, \"to\": 6989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What have been some of your favorite moments so far?\", \"from\": 6992, \"to\": 7044, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your favorite moments\", \"from\": 7015, \"to\": 7036}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ALLYSON FELIX: Yes, of course, those have been really special, just cheering everyone on.\", \"from\": 7046, \"to\": 7135, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ALLYSON FELIX\", \"from\": 7046, \"to\": 7059}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 7069, \"to\": 7075}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 7123, \"to\": 7131}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the first time, I got to go out to gymnastics.\", \"from\": 7137, \"to\": 7187, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 7141, \"to\": 7155}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 7176, \"to\": 7186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I got to watch Simone Biles win another gold medal, and I got to bring my daughter.\", \"from\": 7189, \"to\": 7272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7204, \"end\": 7216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another gold medal\", \"from\": 7221, \"to\": 7239}, {\"ngram\": \"my daughter\", \"from\": 7260, \"to\": 7271}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that was just a highlight for me, watching these Games through her eyes.\", \"from\": 7274, \"to\": 7350, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a highlight\", \"from\": 7287, \"to\": 7303}, {\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 7321, \"to\": 7332}, {\"ngram\": \"her eyes\", \"from\": 7341, \"to\": 7349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been so incredibly special and fun.\", \"from\": 7352, \"to\": 7392, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And so we have really enjoyed that.\", \"from\": 7394, \"to\": 7429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"AMNA NAWAZ: Allyson Felix, we can not thank you enough for taking the time to chat with us.\", \"from\": 7431, \"to\": 7522, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7431, \"end\": 7441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amna_Nawaz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AMNA NAWAZ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amna_Nawaz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amna_Nawaz\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 7497, \"to\": 7505}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 7519, \"to\": 7521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Really appreciate it.\", \"from\": 7524, \"to\": 7545, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Take care.\", \"from\": 7547, \"to\": 7557, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"care\", \"from\": 7552, \"to\": 7556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ALLYSON FELIX: Thank you for having me.\", \"from\": 7559, \"to\": 7598, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ALLYSON FELIX\", \"from\": 7559, \"to\": 7572}]}, {\"se